Lorenzo Battagion</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/luca-casalin/" rel="tag">Luca Casalin</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/opera-lirica/" rel="tag">Opera lirica</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/otello/" rel="tag">Otello</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/salvatore-cordella/" rel="tag">salvatore cordella</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/samantha-korbey/" rel="tag">Samantha Korbey</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/seung-pil-choi/" rel="tag">Seung Pil Choi</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/teatro-regio-di-torino/" rel="tag">Teatro Regio di Torino</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/walter-sutcliffe/" rel="tag">Walter Sutcliffe</a><meta itemprop="keywords" content="ambrogio maestri, Emilio Marcucci, Erika Grimaldi, Gianandrea Noseda, Giuseppe Verdi, Gregory Kunde, Lorenzo Battagion, Luca Casalin, Opera lirica, Otello, salvatore cordella, Samantha Korbey, Seung Pil Choi, Teatro Regio di Torino, Walter Sutcliffe"> </span> </footer></div> </article><div id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/e815c56665d91cc0feb9dea3e3c28ca4" alt="" /> <img src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/giordano-cavagnino-100x150.jpg" width="67" height="100" alt="Giordano Cavagnino" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Giordano Cavagnino"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/giordano-cavagnino/">View all articles by Giordano Cavagnino</a></div></div><div class="nav